### Crear producto con variantes (color + talla)
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Camiseta Premium",
  "description": "Camiseta de algodón peinado con varias tallas y colores.",
  "short_description": "Camiseta premium unisex.",
  "price": 50,
  "sku": "CAM",
  "stock_status": "in_stock",
  "stock_quantity": 0,
  "manage_stock": false,
  "type": "variable",
  "physical_attributes": {
    "length": 30,
    "width": 20,
    "height": 2,
    "weight": 0.2
  },
  "variantes": [
    {
      "color": "Blanco",
      "talla": "S",
      "stock": 50,
      "precio_adicional": 10,
      "imagenes": [
        "https://cdn.tienda.com/cam-blanco-s-1.jpg",
        "https://cdn.tienda.com/cam-blanco-s-2.jpg"
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "Negro",
      "talla": "M",
      "stock": 25,
      "precio_adicional": 5,
      "imagenes": [
        "https://cdn.tienda.com/cam-negro-m-1.jpg"
      ],
      "physical_attributes": {
        "weight": "220g"
      }
    }
  ],
  "image": ""
}

### Actualizar variantes de producto variable
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/69ca244bec3087831395a860
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "variable",
  "variantes": [
    {
      "color": "Blanco",
      "talla": "L",
      "stock": 40,
      "precio_adicional": 12,
      "imagenes": [
        "https://cdn.tienda.com/cam-blanco-l-1.jpg"
      ]
    },
    {
      "color": "Azul",
      "talla": "M",
      "stock": 30,
      "precio_adicional": 8,
      "imagenes": [
        "https://cdn.tienda.com/cam-azul-m-1.jpg"
      ],
      "physical_attributes": {
        "weight": 0.25
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Actualizar solo atributos físicos padre (las variantes sin physical_attributes heredarán estos valores)
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/69ca244bec3087831395a860
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "physical_attributes": {
    "length": 32,
    "width": 21,
    "height": 2,
    "weight": 0.22
  }
}